description:
What happens if a PELIKAN loves a PELIKAN? Yes.. new PELIKANE are born. This is the second PELIKANE collection.

The first collection is already sold out.

24 cute little "second generation PELIKANE" are waiting for a new owner. Be kind to them.

Every "PELIKAN" is made with love.

They are small They are weak

Protect the "PELIKANE"; protect the second generation.
name: PELIKANE - second generation
